# Winding Test


## Resistance

- Winding Resist.
- Temperature Correction


## Insulation

- Ins. Resist.
- Polarization Index


## Ratio

- Turn Ratio
- Phase Displacement


## Analysis

- Vector Group
- SFRA
- Frequency Response
